    <item>
      <title>议长约翰逊在谈判陷入僵局时推动仅限共和党的边境法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/speaker-johnson-pushes-gop-only-border-bill-as-talks-hit-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，众议院议长迈克·约翰逊(Mike Johnson)深入探讨了共和党的立法，民主党人认为该法案在确保美国与墨西哥边境安全方面走得太远，两党就移民问题达成协议的前景变得黯淡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/speaker-johnson-pushes-gop-only-border-bill-as-talks-hit-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 22:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默在英国“选举年”打响发令枪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/uk-labour-party-leader-keir-starmer-fires-starting-gun-on-election-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）将在人们普遍预期的英国大选年向选民发表开场演讲，宣称英国在保守党政府执政 14 年后“迫切需要变革”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/uk-labour-party-leader-keir-starmer-fires-starting-gun-on-election-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求美国最高法院推翻科罗拉多州选票禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/trump-asks-us-supreme-court-to-overturn-colorado-ballot-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 要求美国最高法院推翻一项禁止他参加科罗拉多州总统选举的裁决，从而就他在 2021 年 1 月 6 日国会大厦袭击事件中所扮演的角色是否会导致他丧失任职资格展开了一场历史性的对决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/trump-asks-us-supreme-court-to-overturn-colorado-ballot-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 21:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
